[EN]

Short description of the new agent

* 28 Frames
* Frame #01 is idle frame
* Frames #01-04 contain the initial animations for starting a movement
* Frames #05-28 are the basic walkcycle (which can be looped)

ANGLES

0 (degrees) = west to east
60 (degrees) = southwest to northeast
120 (degrees) = southeast to northwest
180 (degrees) = east to west
240 (degrees) = northeast to southwest
300 (degrees) = northwest to southeast

[DE]

Kurzanleitung der Walkcycle:

Die Walkcycle bestehen aus 28 Frames.

Frame 01 ist der Standframe.
Die Frames 01-04 sind die Anfangsbewegung aus dem Stand heraus
Frame 05-24 sind der eigentliche Walkcycle und dadurch unendlich aneinander reihbar

